{"tid":1217612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳］白宮、回收共狗外籍等聯署整合post","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T19:26:52.000Z","uid":142332,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e59a18e5e1317342e17c7a4f93d3228c55babbe9","tid":1217612,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hackmd.io/@cVs-TFcORpGDecMvspTRBA/S16qeFk1S\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhackmd.io%2F%40cVs-TFcORpGDecMvspTRBA%2FS16qeFk1S&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=7bd30337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hackmd.io/@cVs-TFcORpGDecMvspTRBA/S16qeFk1S</a><br />\n<br />\n其中較重要既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n聯署清單</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首三個是白宮聯署,有簽了的人表示:確認電郵有機會在簽後大約一小時才收到<br />\n1.Reject Immigration or Non-Immigration Visas of Hong Kong Government Officials violating human rights<br />\n收回違反人權的官員的移民權利或旅遊簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/reject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Freject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=cb1d88ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/reject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights</a><br />\n<br />\n2.Revoke the U.S. Citizenship and Visas of the Hong Kong and China Officials who are in Support of the Extradition Bill.<br />\n收回支持修定引渡條例官員的居留權/移民權利/旅遊簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frevoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=174678b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill</a><br />\n<br />\n3.Extradition Law Amendment in Hong Kong - Threat to Personal Safety and Freedom<br />\n有關修定引渡條例會威脅香港居民的個人安全和自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=b04c877f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n4.全球聯署【反送中 民意不可欺 為香港企硬】Global Signing: Against Extradition to China<br />\n反對修訂引渡條例 希望政府能夠聆聽市民意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%A3%E7%B7%9A-civil-human-rights-front-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%AC%BA-%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E7%A1%AC-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=54590810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china</a><br />\n<br />\n集氣呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/